^ a b c "Rankin Smith, 72, the Owner Of the Falcons". The New York Times. 1997-10-27. Retrieved 2008-08-15. 
^ "Welcome to Chi Phi at Auburn University! The Mu Delta Chapter". Chi Phi Fraternity. 2007. Archived from the original on February 5, 2008. Retrieved 2008-08-15. 
^ Bowden, Yvette (2005-12-10). "Life Insurance Company of Georgia". New Georgia Encyclopedia. Georgia Humanities Council and the University of Georgia Press. Retrieved 2008-08-15. 
^ Lowry, Tom (2003-01-27). "The NFL Machine". Business Week. Archived from the original on 2008-07-24. Retrieved 2008-08-15. 
^ "Now Showing". Fernbank Museum of Natural History. Archived from the original on 2008-08-15. Retrieved 2008-08-15. 
