Insider Activity


Individual




Rankin M. Smith



Mr. Rankin M. Smith, Jr., is a Manager & Owner at Seminole Plantation and Independent Director at Fidelity Southern Corp. He is on the Board of Directors at Archbold Medical Center, Archbold Foundation, Fidelity Southern Corp., and Fidelity Bank (Norcross, Georgia).
Mr. Smith was previously employed as Chairman by Thomas University. He also served on the board at Atlanta Falcons Football Club LLC.



